    "name": "Shadow Strike",
    "type": "spell",
    "img": "icons/weapons/swords/sword-broad-serrated-blue.webp",
    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You brandish your weapons or begin casting a spell, only to disappear in a burst of shadows or magical energy. You strike, then immediately teleport to your original position again.</em></p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong></p><p>You can use a hand that's holding a weapon to perform the somatic component of this spell.</p><ul><li><p>You teleport up to 30 ft. to an unoccupied space on the ground, use your action to use your &amp;reference[attack] action (or a cantrip or other offensive action) against a target within range. Once you have finished attacking your target (or targets, if you have multiple), you teleport to your original position.</p></li><li><p>Your first attack on this turn has advantage.</p></li></ul><p></p></div></div><p><em>Overall, <strong>this spell uses both your action and bonus action</strong>. You cannot use more than one spell slot in a turn, as usual, so your action cannot be a spell of 1st level or higher.</em></p>",
            "chat": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong></p><p>You can use a hand that's holding a weapon to perform the somatic component of this spell.</p><ul><li><p>You teleport up to 30 ft. to an unoccupied space on the ground, use your action to use your &amp;reference[attack] action (or a cantrip or other offensive action) against a target within range. Once you have finished attacking your target (or targets, if you have multiple), you teleport to your original position.</p></li><li><p>Your first attack on this turn has advantage.</p></li></ul><p></p></div></div><p><em>Overall, <strong>this spell uses both your action and bonus action</strong>. You cannot use more than one spell slot in a turn, as usual, so your action cannot be a spell of 1st level or higher.</em></p>"
        },
